metadata.name: The Poker Scene
metadata.description:
Storytelling is everything. 

Holiday, Founder of the IMMADEGEN Collection, asked members of his community to envision the backstory of their favorite VOID for a chance to be featured in an iconic digital scene. 

Holiday's goal was to interpret NFT ownership into a piece of art, which is an apologue centered around provenance.

Each of these seven infamous VOID characters has a collector behind it, taking on the personalities and origin stories crafted by their individual owners.

The artistic production encapsulates the collaborative spirit and imagination of their metaverse tribe. Together they have co-created a digital relic of the VOID culture and has become symbolic of the early days of NFT history.

Pioneers, enthusiasts and degens gathered around a table, sharing a moment, conversing and connecting with one another.
